Day 6: Focus on Value!
💡 "The team’s goal isn’t to complete tasks, but to deliver value!"  
👉 Tip: Always steer the conversation toward the value being delivered to customers, not just the number of completed stories.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
